<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFLowi1972" class="citation journal cs1">Lowi, Theodore J. (1972). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/974990">"Four Systems of Policy, Politics, and Choice"</a>. <i>Public Administration Review</i>. <b>32</b> (4): <span class="nowrap">298–</span>310. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F974990">10.2307/974990</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.worldcat.org/issn/0033-3352">0033-3352</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/974990">974990</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Public+Administration+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Four+Systems+of+Policy%2C+Politics%2C+and+Choice&amp;rft.volume=32&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=298-310&amp;rft.date=1972&amp;rft.issn=0033-3352&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F974990%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F974990&amp;rft.aulast=Lowi&amp;rft.aufirst=Theodore+J.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F974990&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATheodore+J.+Lowi" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-7">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFLowi1964" class="citation journal cs1">Lowi, Theodore J. (July 1964). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/world-politics/article/abs/american-business-public-policy-casestudies-and-political-theory/6621C1B577BB52D00AFBD70F82B94C2D">"American Business, Public Policy, Case-Studies, and Political Theory"</a>. <i>World Politics</i>. <b>16</b> (4): <span class="nowrap">677–</span>715. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F2009452">10.2307/2009452</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.worldcat.org/issn/1086-3338">1086-3338</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2009452">2009452</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:154980260">154980260</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=World+Politics&amp;rft.atitle=American+Business%2C+Public+Policy%2C+Case-Studies%2C+and+Political+Theory&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=677-715&amp;rft.date=1964-07&amp;rft.issn=1086-3338&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A154980260%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F2009452%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F2009452&amp;rft.aulast=Lowi&amp;rft.aufirst=Theodore+J.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fworld-politics%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Famerican-business-public-policy-casestudies-and-political-theory%2F6621C1B577BB52D00AF